_sText:
This is my first map.

It is for the mod Jailbreak or Hosties

It features 12 Jail Cells, 1 VIP Room, Infirmary, Crush Box, Large Glass Cage,Very Deep Pool, Armory, Hidden Items/Areas.

Update #1:
Added An Outside Area With A Shot For Shot Area And Added Jump Rope

Added A New Sniping Area

Update #2
Ammo In Guns Fixed
Added A Vent From The Cage To Armory

If there is something wrong tell me and I will try to fix it.
